{"tid":1758912,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉迷思之「Q票」  為何J19馮德森飲恨","createTime":"2019-11-27T10:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T14:29:25.000Z","uid":70194,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84ad45ad18a6c99589524defa2691a5f9bff6dd2","tid":1758912,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"可能有少少遲又或者好多人都知又或者有少少長......<br />\n<br />\n選舉工程本來涉及繁複的程序, 單就點票而言, 負責點票的同事會把所有印章蓋在選票圈內的票視作「有效選票」, 而其他情況 (例如: 印有tendered/spoilt/unused的票、未經填畫、印出界、印落候選人資料/相、印幾十萬個印) 則視作<strong>「問題選票」(即直播時成日聽到的「Q票」[Questionable票])</strong>.<br />\n<br />\n選舉主任會當下逐張「Q票」判斷是否為「有效選票」。考慮基礎為 <span style=\"color: red;\">1) 是否有清晰的投票意向, 2) 會否藉此識別選民身份</span>. 故此，印幾十萬個印、印出圈、Tick號反轉等一般會被視作有清晰的投票意向，是「有效選票」。 另一方面，使用自己攜帶的文具而非官方提供的印章，此做法可被識別選民身份，故即使有清晰的投票意向也會被視作「廢票」。<br />\n<br />\n新聞提到很多選區原先是A君贏B君幾百票，但重點後B君反勝，相信是故意製造話題。很大機會是在未考慮到「Q票」的情況下，A君贏B君。但經考慮所有「Q票」後，B君最終反勝。<br />\n<br />\n最有趣的地方相信是....... 為甚麼有這麼多「Q票」呢? 我相信這不言而喻了。 可以看到，<span style=\"color: red;\">選舉事務處的考慮「Q票」安排是讓學歷較低 / 視力較低 的人有一個投票的機會</span>，讓他們也有發聲及表達自己意見的機會。<br />\n<br />\n但諗深一層，<span style=\"color: red;\">這班人是否真的知道自己在投甚麼</span>？這是另一個要思考的地方了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/731jBW8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F731jBW8.jpg&h=c6b5dc70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖Link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100most/photos/a.292832474177740/2472886709505628/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100most%2Fphotos%2Fa.292832474177740%2F2472886709505628%2F&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=baf04fba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100most/photos/a.292832474177740/2472886709505628/</a>"},{"pid":"fc523a2ee33e3ec23e792956e0d114b3da1fea16","tid":1758912,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"To be fair 咁講<br />\n<br />\n肯定有公公婆婆投泛民但都係印錯位<br />\n<br />\n投票好似好簡單<br />\n<br />\n但的確有啲人會印錯位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df14375132a61de49c30bb2a60425f095261a62","tid":1758912,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc523a2ee33e3ec23e792956e0d114b3da1fea16","tid":1758912,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"To be fair 咁講<br />\n<br />\n肯定有公公婆婆投泛民但都係印錯位<br />\n<br />\n投票好似好簡單<br />\n<br />\n但的確有啲人會印錯位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"但可以倒番轉咁講<br />\n<br />\n根本唔少廢老都唔知入去做咩<br />\n只係有人教佢只要印喺指定 no. 嘅範圍就得<br />\n<br />\n所以我完全覺得個 &quot;tick&quot; 唔喺白圈入面<br />\n根本就應該當廢票<br />\n<br />\n因為佢投票嘅規則都無遵守"},{"pid":"f24d185cf79844852fe34077fc4f57ecb3cf86b9","tid":1758912,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:22:36.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：我地今鋪無輸的念頭<br />\n<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家80%, 仲差少少</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=e1cf7858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=afdbadcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n.<br />\n(對唔住，雖然區選迎來短暫的勝利，但要做ge 野都要持績落去，唔好放軟手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足，星期四愛丁堡見)"},{"pid":"c80579601dbdad0f43fb72ad1eec8619bb21d59e","tid":1758912,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2df14375132a61de49c30bb2a60425f095261a62","tid":1758912,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc523a2ee33e3ec23e792956e0d114b3da1fea16","tid":1758912,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"To be fair 咁講<br />\n<br />\n肯定有公公婆婆投泛民但都係印錯位<br />\n<br />\n投票好似好簡單<br />\n<br />\n但的確有啲人會印錯位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"但可以倒番轉咁講<br />\n<br />\n根本唔少廢老都唔知入去做咩<br />\n只係有人教佢只要印喺指定 no. 嘅範圍就得<br />\n<br />\n所以我完全覺得個 &quot;tick&quot; 唔喺白圈入面<br />\n根本就應該當廢票<br />\n<br />\n因為佢投票嘅規則都無遵守"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"好啦，咁究竟遊戲規則係咪要嚮白圈入面<br />\n<br />\n如果啲人有老花印出界但又明確投票意向點計"},{"pid":"43fd96dcccecaa89307499daf841a3b973fbf39e","tid":1758912,"uid":59700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc523a2ee33e3ec23e792956e0d114b3da1fea16","tid":1758912,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"To be fair 咁講<br />\n<br />\n肯定有公公婆婆投泛民但都係印錯位<br />